article:
This is a 'list of [[amphibious warfare ships]] of the [[United States Navy]]'.
Ship status is indicated as either currently active [A], inactive [I], or
precommissioning [P]. Ships in the inactive category include all that have been
decommissioned. Ships in the precommissioning category include ships under
construction. All information is sourced from the relevant articles.
